<h3>Output:</h3>

<p>The 3! possible permutations with 3 elements:</p>

<p>1 2 3 <br>
1 3 2 <br>
2 1 3 <br>
2 3 1 <br>
3 1 2 <br>
3 2 1 <br></p>

<h4>注意</h4>

<p>当输出{1, 1, 1}的全排列时只输出一组“1 1 1”；</p>

<h3>Complexity</h3>

<blockquote><p>At most, performs one half as many swaps as the number of elements in the range.</p></blockquote>
